Pioneer DEH-150MPG Car CD Player

Pioneer DEH-150MPG Car CD Player - play all your favourite CDs & get a new, advanced level of FM & AM reception with the new Supertuner IIID digital tuner. The Pioneer DEH-150 comes with a built-in MOSFET 50 x 4 amplifier for excellent sound & power. Also featuring a 3-band parametric EQ, EEQ , a selectable fader & 3-mode loudness control let you adjust the music. The Pioneer DEH-150 also has an LCD display & Detachable Front panel for added security. 

features & benefits of the Pioneer DEH-150MPG
 - MP3/CD Tuner - WAV & WMA File Compatible 
- Steering Wheel Control Compatible
 - Front Aux-in (3.5mm Jack plug for MP3 Player)
 - Green Illumination
 -1x Pre-out
 - ID3 Tags Text + Scroll
 - 5 Band EQ
 - Mosfet 4x 50w Output 

whats in the box
- Pioneer DEH-150MPG
- 2 x Release Keys
- 1 x Cage
- 1 x Wiring Loom
- 1 x Front Panel Case
- 1 x Owners Manual
